text: Lucienne Rouet (born 1901, date of death unknown) was a French swimmer. She competed in the women's 100 metre backstroke event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1901 births Category:Year of death missing Category:French female swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of France Category:Swimmers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
